大氣污染與氣候變遷                      


  	課程學習目標 Course goal
1. 培養學生對氣候變遷議題專業知識。
2. 培養學生思考解決大氣污染、氣候變遷相關議題。
3. 培養學生對大氣污染科學知識。
4. 培養學生應用大氣知識，利用擴散傳輸機制解決空氣污染問題之能力。 
課程進度 Course Progress Outline
週次 Week 進度說明 Progress Description 
1 Introduction 
2 Introduction to Atmosphere 
3 Atmospheric Pollution (1): Aerosol 
4 Atmospheric Pollution (2): Acid Rain 
5 Atmospheric Pollution (3): Photochemical Smog 
6 Atmospheric Pollution (4): Air Toxics 
7 校際週 
8 Diffusion Theory 
9 Air Pollution Meteorology 
10 Plume Rise 
11 Atmospheric Dispersion Modeling 
12 Gaussian Model Application 
13 Stratospheric Ozone Layer 
14 Introduction to Climate Change 
15 International Program for Climate Change 
16 Mitigation Strategy for Climate Change 
17 Adaptation Strategy for Climate Change 
18 Presentation/ Final Exam 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.
