課程學習目標 Course Objectives
培養學生對氣候變遷議題專業知識培養學生思考解決大氣污染、氣候變遷相關議題培養學生對大氣污染科學知識培養學生應用大氣知識，利用擴散傳輸機制解決空氣污染問題之能力培養學生應用大氣知識，利用擴散傳輸機制解決氣候變遷問題之能力 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction2Introduction to Atmosphere3Aerosol4Photochemical Smog5Acid Rain & Air Toxics6Weather Systems and Atmospheric Parameters on Air Motion7Air Pollution Meteorology8Diffusion Theory & Plume Rise9Oral Presentation (I)10Gaussian Model11Gaussian Model Application12Advanced Models (Physical /Receptor/ Numerical)13Stratospheric Ozone Layer14Introduction to Climate Change15International Program on Climate Change16Adaptation Program17Mitigation Program18Oral Presentation (II) 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


